"title": "4504: roots",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4504",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The source and foundation of a tree or plant, anchoring it to the soil, usually found beneath the surface of the ground. Scripture contains literal, metaphorical and figurative references to roots.</p>\n<h2>Roots of trees and plants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:4\">JOB 30:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:7-Job14:9\">JOB 14:7–14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:3-Matt13:6\">MAT 13:3–13:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:2-Mark4:6\">MRK 4:2–4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:20-Mark11:21\">MRK 11:20–11:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as the ``Root of David''</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:1–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:10-Isa11:12\">ISA 11:10–11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:1-Isa53:3\">ISA 53:1–53:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:8-Rom15:12\">ROM 15:8–15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:5\">REV 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>The metaphorical use of roots</h2>\n<h3>Individuals and nations depicted as trees or plants with roots</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:18-Job29:20\">JOB 29:18–29:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:14\">JDG 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:11-Job8:19\">JOB 8:11–8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:5-Job18:17\">JOB 18:5–18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:14-Ps80:15\">PSA 80:14–80:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:22-Isa5:24\">ISA 5:22–5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:30\">ISA 14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:30-Isa37:32\">ISA 37:30–37:32</a> <em>the LORD's sign to Hezekiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7-Jer17:8\">JER 17:7–17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:1-Ezek17:10\">EZK 17:1–17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:3-Ezek31:9\">EZK 31:3–31:9</a>DAN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:13-Ezek4:16\">4:13–4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:23-Dan4:26\">DAN 4:23–4:26</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:16\">HOS 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:5\">HOS 14:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:1\">MAL 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:10\">MAT 3:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:9\">LUK 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:18-Matt13:21\">MAT 13:18–13:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:13-Mark4:17\">MRK 4:13–4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:11-Luke8:13\">LUK 8:11–8:13</a> <em>the parable of the sower</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:13\">MAT 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:13-Rom11:21\">ROM 11:13–11:21</a></p>\n<h3>Sources and foundations described as roots</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:28\">JOB 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:9\">JOB 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:12\">PRO 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:29\">ISA 14:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:9\">AMO 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:6\">JON 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>Bitter roots</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:15\">HEB 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:18\">DEU 29:18</a></p>\n<h2>Roots as a symbol of stability and growth</h2>\n<h3>Taking root</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:6-Col2:7\">COL 2:6–2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:30\">2KI 19:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:3\">JOB 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:8-Ps80:9\">PSA 80:8–80:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:6\">ISA 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:24\">ISA 40:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:2\">JER 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:14-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:14–3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Being uprooted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:10\">JOB 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:15\">1KI 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:5\">PSA 52:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:30\">PRO 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:3\">PRO 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:10\">JER 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:14-Jer12:15\">JER 12:14–12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:28\">JER 31:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer45:4\">JER 45:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:9\">EZK 17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:12\">EZK 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12\">JUD 1:12</a></p>",
